---
import Verdant from "../layouts/Verdant.astro";
import Footer from "../components/verdant/Footer";
---

<Verdant title="Terms of Service — Verdant">
  <main style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem) clamp(20px, 5vw, 56px);">
    <h1 style="font-size: var(--text-3xl); color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; font-size: var(--text-base); line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted);">
      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Beta Access</h2>
        <p>Garden is in early access. We're still building. Things may break, change, or disappear. We'll do our best to keep your data safe.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Your Responsibility</h2>
        <p>You're responsible for keeping your password secure. We can't recover it for you — it's encrypted so we can't even read it.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 1rem;">What We're Not</h2>
        <p>Garden is not investment advice, tax advice, or financial advice. We show you your numbers. What you do with them is your call.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Limits on Liability</h2>
        <p>If something goes wrong, we'll fix it. But we're not responsible for your financial decisions, data loss due to you forgetting your password, or any indirect damages.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Questions?</h2>
        <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:verdantmail@proton.me" style="color: var(--green); text-decoration: underline;">verdantmail@proton.me</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer client:visible />
</Verdant>
